Name: :math:`p_{\text{node}}`
Description: Real power injection (or load) at bus :math:`i`

Name: :math:`q_{\text{node}}`
Description: Reactive power injection (or load) at bus :math:`i`

Name: :math:`i_{\max}`
Description: Maximum allowable current magnitude at bus :math:`i`

Name: :math:`v_{\min}`
Description: Minimum voltage level (per unit) at bus :math:`i`

Name: :math:`v_{\max}`
Description: Maximum voltage level (per unit) at bus :math:`i`

Name: :math:`d^{\text{master}}`
Description: Binary indicator: 1 if active and for notactive 0

Name: :math:`M`
Description: Big-M constant used in voltage drop constraints
